Package milestone2

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    LuxValueListener
    Interface that will implment a simple listener for the Lux Value.
    SparqlListener
    Interface that will implment a simple listener for the SPARQL lux values.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LEDActor
    Class that handles the LED on a specific GPIO on the PI.
    LuxRessource
    Handles a Ressource that will send the Lux Value that is been read by the Arduino.
    Milestone2
    Milestone 2 will connect to an SSP and send all the information of the sensors.
    PhotoSensor
    This is a simple Photosensor that is read by the Arduino and the Arduino send it by serial Port.
    Ressource<T>
    This is a superclass of all the Ressources for the SSP.
    SimpleCallback
    This is a very simple implementation of ClientCallback which does virtually nothing but log internal events.
    SPARQLConnector
    This is the Connector for the SPARQL Endpoint which will receive the values of all the LDR's of all the other Groups.
    SSPServer  
    TimeRessource
    This Webresource updates on a regular basis and provides the current UTC-time.
